<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT76">
<l>pāṭṭu muṟaiyum paṭukataiyum palporuḷu</l>
<l>mīṭṭiya tīyu miruvicumpuṅ kēṭṭa</l>
<l>maṉuvum curuti maṟaiṉāṉku māyaṉ</l>
<l>ṟaṉamāyai yiṟpaṭṭa taṟpu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Poetry and ordered [texts], excellent stories, and the many meanings,</l>
<l>The acquired fire, the wide sky,</l>
<l>The Manu [smṛti], and the four aural Vedas that are heard</l>
<l>are [elements] whose real nature came into existence</l>
<l rend="indent">through the māyā of the wondrous [Lord].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
